{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b829b6d83b","title":"致彭德怀电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"07896d04cc","index":0,"year":1936,"month":10,"day":10,"articleId":"b829b6d83b"}],"tags":[{"id":"ae0a6697a5","name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji9-1","name":"毛泽东全集第9卷(1)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji9-1.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji9-1":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a70263dd7e","type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"b829b6d83b"},{"id":"c83dbc4ca8","type":"paragraph","text":"（1936年10月10日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"b829b6d83b"},{"id":"d5ec6b13d2","type":"paragraph","text":"朱、张已到会宁，询问见面人员与地点，中央已复。我们意见，以兄西去就他们为宜。朱、张来电称中央及毛、周、彭，自称西北军委，又一电称执行毛、周、彭所示任务，亦事实上承认我们军委。我们方面曾有两电去，称朱总司令、张总政委，以后即照此种方式解决，以便顺利执行宁夏战役。朱、张以两总名义，依照中央写军委之决定指挥各军作战。为便之增加对于执行军事任务之坚决性，防止可能的动摇性（在目前是防止对宁夏战役之某种可能的动摇），兄须加以特别之注意","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"b829b6d83b"},{"id":"9302c29d5c","type":"paragraph","text":"见面时对老问题请一概不谈。[1]这是毛泽东致彭德怀电的主要内容。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"b829b6d83b"}],"page":{"id":"e32bb471f1","publicationId":"maoquanji9-1","articleId":"b829b6d83b","start":212,"end":212}}}},"__N_SSG":true}